window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Watch out for the road weenies! </p> <p>A town is overrun by road weenies - a.k.a. joggers - who never smile. A girl thinks she's too old for Halloween...until she finds a special pair of gloves. A boy takes a shortcut to an unexpected place. A mummy takes his revenge, one little piece at a time.... </p> <p>Welcome to the weird and wacky world of award-winning storyteller and master of the macabre, David Lubar. These 35 tales ranging from the silly and offbeat to flat-out horrifying are just right for listening alone in the dark. As an added bonus at the end of the book, David answers the question most frequently asked of writers with a behind-the-scenes look at the various ways he got the ideas for the stories in this collection. </p> <p>Don't be a weenie. Listen to these stories. <i>If you dare!</i></p>"; 
